# âš¡ Sandevistan

> **Decode macOS crashes in seconds, not hours**

Stop staring at cryptic crash logs. Sandevistan uses AI to translate Apple IPS crash files into plain English explanationsâ€”instantly.

```bash
sandevistan analyze crash.ips  # or 'sandy' for short
# âœ¨ Get human-readable crash analysis powered by Google Gemini Flash
```

