## ğŸ› ï¸ Development

### Local development
```bash
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/Dil4rd/sandevistan.git
cd sandevistan

# Run without installation (use 'sandy' or 'sandevistan')
uvx --from . sandy analyze crash.ips

# Install in editable mode
uv pip install -e .
```

